{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-282-the-ackermann-function","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 282: Ackermannova funkcija","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Za neujemne celobrojke $m$, $n$, Ackerman funkcija $A(m, n)$ je definisana na sledeći način:</p>\n<p>$$A(m, n) =\n\\begin{cases}\nn + 1                 &#x26; \\text{ikiwa $m = 0$}             \\\\\nA(m - 1, 1)           &#x26; \\text{ikiwa $m > 0$ na $n = 0$} \\\\\nA(m - 1, A(m, n - 1)) &#x26; \\text{ikiwa $m > 0$ na $n > 0$}\n\\end{cases}$$</p>\n<p>Na primer $A(1, 0) = 2$, $A(2, 2) = 7$ i $A(3, 4) = 125$.</p>\n<p>Izračunaj $\\displaystyle\\sum_{n = 0}^6 A(n, n)$ za vaš odgovor po modulo ${14}^8$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4861000cf542c50ff99","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301933,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-282-the-ackermann-function"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function ackermanFunction() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nackermanFunction();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>ackermanFunction()</code> treba da vrati <code>1098988351</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(ackermanFunction(), 1098988351);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-201-to-300","dashedName":"problem-282-the-ackermann-function","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler